OL,5,G0800 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,6,     FWe meet Tracey and Mike, who run
OL,7,     Ftwo bars on the Costa Del Sol. The
OL,8,     Ffirst was bought from its original
OL,9,     Fowner on an especially good night
OL,10,     Fduring a holiday four years ago!
OL,11,G0900 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,12,     FMeet Joe and Jan, a couple of
OL,13,     Fwell-loved characters who have
OL,14,     Fbeen married for 49 years and will
OL,15,     Fbe familiar to fans.
OL,16,G1000 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,17,     FKate's tenants are suing her for
OL,18,     Ftrying to evict them. After a
OL,19,     Fhealth scare, Tim wants to sell
OL,20,     Fhis property, but his tenant
OL,21,     Frefuses to leave.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
