OL,5,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FInterceptor Martin clocks a driver
OL,7,     Fsmashing the speed limit at more
OL,8,     Fthan 100mph. Soon banged to rights
OL,9,     Fin the back of the cop car, the
OL,10,     Fdriver gets lippy.
OL,11,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,12,     FWhen his girlfriend is taken away,
OL,13,     Fa drunk driver shows his true
OL,14,     Fcolours by propositioning
OL,15,     FInterceptor Sophie, who is
OL,16,     Funimpressed with his moves.
