OL,5,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FSteve responds to a burglary in
OL,7,     Fprogress, chasing a suspect
OL,8,     Fthrough back gardens. Interceptors
OL,9,     Fflood a housing estate searching
OL,10,     Ffor suspects involved in a
OL,11,     Fshooting.
OL,12,G1700 Call the Bailiffs: Time to Pay Up!
OL,13,     FEnforcement Agent Alex aims to
OL,14,     Fcollect a huge #35k debt, while
OL,15,     FMark and Sam trail a woman who
OL,16,     Fowes more than a year's worth of
OL,17,     Frent - a sizable #25k - to a
OL,18,     Fprevious landlord.
OL,19,G1800 Home and Away
OL,20,     FRichie gets it wrong. Cash
OL,21,     Fstruggles with Eden's decision.
OL,22,     FCrime escalates in Summer Bay.
