OL,5,G1830 Home and Away
OL,6,     FRichie gets another shot. Jo digs
OL,7,     Fherself a deeper hole with Tane.
OL,8,     FTane's called to visit his family.
OL,9,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,10,     FThe healthcare professionals and
OL,11,     Fstaff at the Hall Green Health
OL,12,     FCentre have 26,000 patients on
OL,13,     Ftheir books, with problems ranging
OL,14,     Ffrom sore feet to self-harm.
OL,15,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,16,     FBarnsley's A&E department is put
OL,17,     Funder the microscope. There are
OL,18,     Fcomplications when Wendy, who
OL,19,     Fsuffers from kidney failure, is
OL,20,     Fadmitted with a heart condition.
