OL,5,G2100 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FIn Belfast, a semi-pro boxer is
OL,7,     Frushed to A&E after blacking out
OL,8,     Ffrom heavy blows to the head, with
OL,9,     Ffears of a brain bleed, while an
OL,10,     Felderly patient is rushed in
OL,11,     Fstruggling to breathe.
OL,12,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,13,     FA man is stabbed multiple times,
OL,14,     Frequiring urgent attention and
OL,15,     Ftreatment; a 64-year-old stops
OL,16,     Fbreathing while her husband calls
OL,17,     Fthe hospital.
