OL,6,     FA 20-year-old woman with a
OL,7,     Flifelong auto-immune skin
OL,8,     Fcondition has an adverse reaction
OL,9,     Fduring the healing process of her
OL,10,     Fnew tattoo.
OL,11,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,12,     FThe ambulances are stacking up
OL,13,     Foutside, a patient goes into
OL,14,     Fcardiac arrest, then the fire
OL,15,     Falarm goes off and Sister Benita
OL,16,     FWainwright must lead the
OL,17,     Fevacuation.
OL,18,G0245 Skin A&E
OL,19,     FDr Dev Shah faces an eyeball-sized
OL,20,     Fcyst on a patient's cheek, while
OL,21,     FDr Toby Nelson tries to evict a
OL,22,     Ftroublesome lipoma called Janet.
